A new uncensored promo for Comedy Central&#8217;s &#8220;Broad City&#8221; shows its main characters reacting to the presidential inauguration of Donald Trump.A frightened Abbi and Ilana make sure they have what they need to survive in Trump&#8217;s America in the new video, which sees the panicked friends talk via video call on inauguration day.At T-minus-60 before the inauguration, they question whether mustaches will be important for the apocalypse, make sure they have mace and a butterfly knife and discuss looting batteries and food, then count down the final seconds.-Relaxnews